<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3163] If we timeout PENDING_CLOSE and send another closeRegion RPC, need to handle NSRE from RS (comes as a RemoteException)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3163</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we send a closeRegion RPC to an RS, we are catching NSRE but when the RS is the one throwing the NSRE, then it comes back as a RemoteException (then an NSRE) and we aren&apos;t unwrapping it properly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We need to catch this and then deal with it appropriately.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Still tracking how this happened in the first place.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
